snippet.title: Slenderman Must Run
snippet.description:
Android Download Link: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.PoisonGames.SlendermanMustRun

This time you are the Slenderman and You MUST RUN from Angry Humans!

Run, dash, Jump and Slide, avoid traps and stay alive. 
Watch your steps! While you run, collect the pages!


Five different levels: Sanatorium, Underground Bunker, Silent Streets, Industrial Waste Area and Silent Forest!

Slenderman Endless Run Features:

-Free Running Horror Game
-Fluent screen touch & gravity control
-Super crazy running 
-Beautiful 3D Graphics
-Achievements and Missions!

Join the most Scary Chase!
